I"ó<p>At <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/how-we-scaled-cashboss-500k-downloads-5-months-manas-j-saloi/">CashBoss</a> we used to refresh the revenue page in our dashboard every hour. Everyone in the team had access to all our numbers. As our revenue continued to grow, we got even more obsessed with it. We used to even show our revenue on a big TV. But optimizing on the local maxima did not lead to our business grow by <a href="https://manassaloi.com/2020/01/04/add-a-zero.html">10X</a>.</p>
